'''Winged-stars''' were shelled flying insects native to [[Caluula/Legends|Caluula]]. Every 300 years they emerged in the [[Nocturne of the Winged-Stars]]. However, they were possibly all eliminated in [[29 ABY/Legends|29 ABY]] by the [[Alpha Red (pathogen)|Alpha Red virus]].

